  ],
  "remarks": "JSC “Vologda Optical and Mechanical Plant” (JSC VOMZ) is a diversified machine-building enterprise. It produces complex optoelectronic products and provides the Russian Armed Forces and Ministry of Defence with its products. JSC VOMZ produces scopes VOMZ Pilad BREVIS P2,5x24 which are used in the war of aggression against Ukraine. Moreover, JSC VOMZ openly supports the Russian war in Ukraine by sharing supportive posts on social media. Therefore, JSC VOMZ is supporting materially actions which undermine and threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty and independence of Ukraine.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}